race.description: Mega Jumps Castle & Party Hire Handicap
race.comment: ALTERMATUM (8) returned with an excellent run at Sandown Hillside behind the unbeaten Enamorada, finding the line strongly from back in the field to grab third. The late splits there said she's come back very well and while back in trip here, she is effective over a sprint trip and should be fitter. ESCARPA (6) resumed with a smart win here as favourite, coming from back in the field to score by 1.3 lengths. Bit more depth here but she'll be hard to hold out again. NORMANDY LASS (7) is flying this time in, winning a BM62 here comfortably when last seen after making all. She'll have map favours over some key dangers and should look the winner at some point. SEA POEM (3) was just fair fresh in the Enamorada race but back in trip for her should be suitable. ARTISTIC GENIUS (1) is going okay and will find this easier.
